show.description: A fake wedding, a fiery attraction, and a woman the world misjudged. What starts as a contract between Alicia and Lucius soon ignites into something undeniable. “Billionaire Playboy’s Replacement Bride” delivers heat, heartbreak, and a love that defies the rules.
